<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Chisʋs achukma kʋt
 Pi̱ hullo fehnʋshke;
 Pi okchalinchi hosh
 Pi 'lhtobʋt illi tok;

[C1]
   Chisʋs pi̱ Shahli chia ma!
   E chi aiokpahanchishke.

[V2]
 Pin Chitokaka yosh
 Ʋba anumpa ha̱
 Pihi̱ma tok oka
 Il ahnihinchashke:

[C2]
   Chisʋs pi̱ Shahli chia ma!
   E chi aiokpahanchishke.

[V3]
 Chisʋs im anumpa
 Achukma hatukma
 E haiyaklo kak osh
 Pi yukpa fehnʋshke:

[C3]
   Chisʋs pi̱ Shahli chia ma!
   E chi aiokpahanchashke.

[V4]
 Chisʋs im anumpa't
 Pi chu̱kʋsh fehna ka
 Pi nukfoka tukma,
 Pi okcha̱ya hinla

[C4]
   Chisʋs pi̱ Shahli chia ma!
   E chi aiokpahanchashke.

[V5]
 Chihowa Ushi ma!
 Et ish pi̱ hullashke,
 Pi shilombish oka
 Ish okchalinchashke:

[C5]
   Chisʋs pi̱ Shahli chia ma!
   E chim ilbʋsha fehnʋshke.

[V6]
 Chu̱kʋsh yoshoba ya̱
 Isht ish pi̱ kanchi cha,
 Chu̱kʋsh himona ya̱
 Et ish pihi̱mashke

[C6]
   Chisʋs pi̱ Shahli chia ma.
   E chim ilbʋsha fehnʋshke.</lyrics>
<aka>Chisʋs achukma kʋt</aka>
<time_sig>H.M. (6.6.6.6.8.8.)</time_sig>
<title>Praise the Saviour. ƲIT40</title>
<author>Cyrus Byington</author>
